<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Darkforge Helm Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Head to Cazic Thule and kill Lizardman Crusaders to retrieve a Decaying Helm and a Decaying Visor.<BR>
<BR>
2) Head to East Freeport and kill city guards to retrieve 2 Freeport Militia Helms.<BR>
<BR>
3) Head to the Temple of Solusek Ro and give the items to the Undead Knight. <BR>
<BR>
4) Give him the items and you will receive a Darkforge Helm.</div>
<BR>
