<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Marconius</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-05-24 09:59:03</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Pardon, but Damaged Militia Helms are NOT the same thing. <BR>
They come from Freeport Militia guards, not Lizardmen Crusaders, and the helm and visor you need are decaying not damaged.  As much as I deeply wished you needed Damaged Militia Helms, you do not (also, if your a Dark Elf Shadowknight, Damaged Militia Helms are completely useless unless you want an eternally brown nose)<BR>
<BR>
Marconius Thex<BR>
18th level Shadowknight of Druzzil Ro Dimension.</font></td></tr></table>
